'''Battlegrounds Mobile India International Cup''' (abbreviated as '''BMIC''') is a [[Battlegrounds Mobile India]] international tournament series.

The 2026 edition is the series' second edition organized by [[KRAFTON]] and features a total prize pool of {{TBD}} with the participation of teams from {{FlagNoLink|in}} India, {{FlagNoLink|kr}} South Korea and {{FlagNoLink|jp}} Japan<!--, fighting for spots into the {{LeagueIconSmall/pubg mobile global championship|date=2025-11-01|}} [[PUBG_Mobile_Global_Championship/2026|2026 PMGC]]-->.

